{"tid":1551223,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"時速134公里 紐男坐雲霄飛車在空中抓到手機","createTime":"2019-09-08T01:55:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T05:54:57.000Z","uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"afb34b5e26b2fa10e13eb65bc9ae9ea28d6b06d6","tid":1551223,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T01:55:47.000Z","msg":"紐西蘭一名男子的反應快到不可思議，他上個月在搭乘時速134公里的雲霄飛車時，竟然看到而且在空中接到其他遊客掉落的手機。而他這個超常的動作當時被攝影機記錄下來，現在已經在網上熱傳。<br />\n <br />\n這個名叫肯普夫（Samuel Kempf）的男子來自紐西蘭南島的城市蒂馬魯（Timaru）。他是一名運動員，上個月代表該國前往瑞士參加浮士德球（Fistball）的世界盃比賽。浮士德球源自於歐洲，其規則類似排球，通常在戶外的草地上舉行。<br />\n <br />\n在該項比賽於8月17日結束之後，肯普夫與家人前往西班牙巴塞隆納（Barcelona）遊玩，並造訪冒險港主題公園（PortAventura theme park），體驗一下該景點著名的雲霄飛車。<br />\n <br />\n這個雲霄飛車的行進速度可達每小時134公里，它曾經是歐洲最高和最快的雲霄飛車。光是在地面上看就夠讓人心驚膽跳了，而不要說親自搭乘它。<br />\n <br />\n而心臟很強的肯普夫卻嘗試搭乘這個雲霄飛車，他也因而完成了在行進中從空中抓到手機的創舉。<br />\n <br />\n肯普夫表示，他看到前兩排的遊客掉了iPhone X手機，它先是往上飛，接著掉到該名遊客的車廂底部。他隨後又看到那支手機漂浮在半空中，於是他用右手隨手一抓，就抓到手裡了。<br />\n <br />\n在這趟雲霄飛車之旅結束後，肯普夫將手機交還給失主，讓他又驚又喜。肯普夫說：「他非常驚訝和高興。他給我一個大大的擁抱，而且說要買車上安裝的攝影機所拍攝的短片給我。」<br />\n <br />\n肯普夫於9月4日在YouTube網站上分享了這段短片，如今已經爆紅。他在說明中寫道：「我坐雲霄飛車時在空中抓到陌生人的手機！"},{"pid":"5f0d7f5e19850cb50d3b936756dc28b1aed8143d","tid":1551223,"uid":32511,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T01:56:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d6KNEe_2qDw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dd6KNEe_2qDw&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprvcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=fe9f5021\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d6KNEe_2qDw</a>"},{"pid":"25c5e3df2fe1fbdfd747072f049dd6a539822d02","tid":1551223,"uid":36813,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T01:56:45.000Z","msg":"屌你呢個時間唔好post 垃圾啦<br />\n<br />\n遮打見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd164372d1bf0c05ddd8a45ea0a873db9bb60c2d","tid":1551223,"uid":129012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:32:45.000Z","msg":"而且說要買車上安裝的攝影機所拍攝的短片給我。<br />\n<br />\n咩意思？"},{"pid":"7f39e7c47ff4d108e1b9588d64d5eeca74655715","tid":1551223,"uid":131522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd164372d1bf0c05ddd8a45ea0a873db9bb60c2d","tid":1551223,"uid":129012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:32:45.000Z","msg":"而且說要買車上安裝的攝影機所拍攝的短片給我。<br />\n<br />\n咩意思？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:37:05.000Z","msg":"即係買條回憶片比佢<br />\n有啲機動遊戲有Cam影住"},{"pid":"0d026a766e2bc93dd8d2a13115d8a99a08e517a9","tid":1551223,"uid":129012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f39e7c47ff4d108e1b9588d64d5eeca74655715","tid":1551223,"uid":131522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd164372d1bf0c05ddd8a45ea0a873db9bb60c2d","tid":1551223,"uid":129012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:32:45.000Z","msg":"而且說要買車上安裝的攝影機所拍攝的短片給我。<br />\n<br />\n咩意思？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:37:05.000Z","msg":"即係買條回憶片比佢<br />\n有啲機動遊戲有Cam影住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:40:06.000Z","msg":"屌仲以為做乜冇啦啦買個車cam比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n過山車唔係車？"},{"pid":"68731d3ea0275778e6681cd5293b6e96009feb5f","tid":1551223,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:40:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">警會冇權傳召證人</div></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cr8vCI9d8uM&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCr8vCI9d8uM%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprvcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=ef02cbe6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cr8vCI9d8uM&amp;feature=youtu.be</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" cla